[3399 Days]

62
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:58,067
[Beiyu Tunnel 3 Rescue, Hour 13]

63
00:04:05,233 --> 00:04:06,000
Everyone, hurry up.

64
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,667
Move quickly.

65
00:04:06,667 --> 00:04:08,067
Grab your stuff and follow me, quickly!

66
