67
00:04:10,167 --> 00:04:11,600
We're reporters from Nanwu TV station.

68
00:04:12,267 --> 00:04:13,167
Hurry up!

69
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,433
Catch up, quick!

70
00:04:14,433 --> 00:04:15,600
Don't cross the blockade line.

71
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,467
It's very dangerous there now.

72
00:04:16,467 --> 00:04:17,433
Got it. Thank you.

73
00:04:17,433 --> 00:04:17,933
No need.

74
00:04:17,933 --> 00:04:18,633
Hurry up!

75
00:04:28,433 --> 00:04:29,633
Everyone, remember this,

76
00:04:29,633 --> 00:04:30,633
