86
00:04:54,267 --> 00:04:55,433
A serious mudslide occurred

87
00:04:55,433 --> 00:04:56,600
[First News, All Ears for You]
at Beiyu Tunnel 3.

88
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,367
Currently, it is known

89
00:04:57,367 --> 00:04:59,367
seven vehicles are trapped inside the tunnel.

90
00:04:59,467 --> 00:05:00,500
After the incident,

91
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,667
the municipal government immediately activated the rescue plan.

92
00:05:02,733 --> 00:05:04,133
I will now provide a deeper report.

93
00:05:04,133 --> 00:05:04,800
Miss, please stop!

94
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,567
Yu!

95
00:05:05,567 --> 00:05:06,467
It's dangerous ahead. You can't go in!

96
00:05:06,467 --> 00:05:07,033
She's a family member.

97
00:05:07,033 --> 00:05:07,767
Save my daughter!

98
00:05:07,767 --> 00:05:08,667
Her name is Shi Jiayu!

99
00:05:08,667 --> 00:05:09,767
Family members, please rest to the side.

100
00:05:09,767 --> 00:05:10,833
Please stay calm.

101
00:05:10,833 --> 00:05:11,733
Save my daughter!

102
00:05:11,733 --> 00:05:13,167
If you go in now, it will interfere with our rescue.

103
00:05:13,467 --> 00:05:14,467
Please rest to the side.

104
00:05:14,533 --> 00:05:15,033
Is that okay?

105
00:05:15,367 --> 00:05:16,267
Family members, please rest to the side.

106
00:05:16,267 --> 00:05:17,233
Let's rest over there.

107
00:05:17,233 --> 00:05:17,867
Is that okay?

108
00:05:27,067 --> 00:05:27,733
Yifan,

109
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,467
