110
00:05:30,433 --> 00:05:31,133
Yifan?

111
00:05:32,767 --> 00:05:33,600
What's wrong?

112
00:05:33,933 --> 00:05:34,767
I'm fine.

113
00:05:35,167 --> 00:05:36,367
So far,

114
00:05:36,367 --> 00:05:38,633
[Beiyu Tunnel 3 Rescue]
more than a dozen injured have been successfully rescued.

115
00:05:38,767 --> 00:05:40,133
[Hour 25]
They are being sent to the hospital for treatment.

116
00:05:40,267 --> 00:05:40,933
It is understood

117
00:05:41,067 --> 00:05:42,167
