230
00:10:23,867 --> 00:10:25,367
and three have more severe injuries.

231
00:10:25,367 --> 00:10:26,800
They are currently receiving treatment.

232
00:10:26,967 --> 00:10:28,400
The one most people are concerned about

233
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,633
is seven-year-old girl Shi Jiayu.

234
00:10:29,767 --> 00:10:31,567
She is still under observation in the ICU.

235
00:10:32,067 --> 00:10:33,200
Any latest updates

236
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,400
will be brought to you as soon as possible.

237
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,967
Is Shi Jiayu still in the ICU?

238
00:10:36,067 --> 00:10:36,767
Please wait.

239
00:10:36,767 --> 00:10:37,400
I'll check

240
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,500
